description: The Isle of Man government has published its plan to relax its border restrictions.
title: Coronavirus: Isle of Man five-stage border plan published
title_page: Coronavirus: Isle of Man five-stage border plan published - BBC News
maintext: He added: "I'm aware this will be a relief to some and a frustration to others. But in line with our approach right up to this point, we feel it is better to be cautious."
